25|$|However, because Justice Brennan {{believed}} that <b>the</b> <b>death</b> <b>penalty</b> <b>is</b> in all circumstances {{cruel and unusual}} punishment, he would have vacated Washington's death sentence and remanded for further proceedings.|$|E
